WEBVTT

00:00:36.180 --> 00:00:40.940
=Ancient Bracelet=

00:00:41.340 --> 00:00:44.380
=Episode 22=

00:00:44.420 --> 00:00:46.660
=I Thought I'd Never See You Again=

00:00:48.280 --> 00:00:49.470
The Fengwu Bracelet.

00:00:51.110 --> 00:00:51.950
Ying Du,

00:00:52.163 --> 00:00:53.840
you actually went this far
to protect her.

00:00:54.470 --> 00:00:57.000
You poured all your power
into the Bracelet.

00:01:02.790 --> 00:01:04.000
So,

00:01:04.310 --> 00:01:06.640
this whole thing was your scheme.

00:01:10.510 --> 00:01:12.760
I won't let you harm Ying Du again.

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:26.840
Ying Du,

00:01:27.506 --> 00:01:28.613
what are you planning to do?

00:01:28.920 --> 00:01:29.760
Zhaoli,

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:30.920
wait for my return.

00:01:38.230 --> 00:01:39.150
Ying Du,

00:01:42.200 --> 00:01:44.350
