00:01:45.430 --> 00:01:46.560
Come back.

00:01:48.430 --> 00:01:49.950
Come back now!

00:02:30.560 --> 00:02:32.430
No, impossible.

00:02:32.470 --> 00:02:33.590
How could I possibly die?

00:02:33.910 --> 00:02:34.910
This can't be.

00:02:41.280 --> 00:02:43.030
(Ying Du's power faded away.)

00:02:44.470 --> 00:02:45.310
(Has something)

00:02:46.870 --> 00:02:48.280
(happened to Ying Du?)

00:02:56.840 --> 00:02:57.910
Ying Du!

00:03:10.430 --> 00:03:11.270
Ying Du!

00:03:19.750 --> 00:03:23.940
♪I wish I could hold you once more♪

00:03:28.030 --> 00:03:29.360
You scared me to death.

00:03:29.590 --> 00:03:31.590
I thought I'd never see you again.

00:03:32.680 --> 00:03:33.520
Zhaoli,

00:03:34.080 --> 00:03:34.920
don't be afraid.

00:03:35.720 --> 00:03:38.720
