blurring suddenly♪

00:03:51.660 --> 00:03:56.540
♪Memories turn,
forgiving time after time♪

00:03:58.050 --> 00:04:01.290
♪Tears or snowflakes, sweet or bitter♪

00:04:01.290 --> 00:04:04.130
♪Hard to tell them apart♪

00:04:04.810 --> 00:04:09.990
♪Vowing to give you
three lifetimes' happiness♪

00:04:10.280 --> 00:04:11.120
Ying Du,

00:04:12.840 --> 00:04:14.030
at last, we...

00:04:14.200 --> 00:04:16.420
♪No matter the homeward journey♪

00:04:17.950 --> 00:04:18.790
Ying Du!

00:04:19.480 --> 00:04:20.320
Ying Du!

00:04:22.160 --> 00:04:23.000
Ying Du!

00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:26.490
♪Ahead lies a path without snow or wind♪

00:04:26.510 --> 00:04:27.950
Ying Du, don't scare me like that.

00:04:28.560 --> 00:04:29.600
What's happening to you?

00:04:31.310 --> 00:04:32.920
I'm fine.

00:04:35.390 --> 00:04:36.230
Zhaoli,

00:04:36.870 --> 00:04:37.750
don't cry.

00:04:46.000 --> 00:04:46.840
Your leg...

00:04:47.310 --> 00:04:48.430
Your body...

00:04:49.830 --> 00:04:51.310
