00:04:52.240 --> 00:04:53.080
Zhaoli,

00:04:54.950 --> 00:04:56.720
you're crying for me again.

00:04:57.560 --> 00:05:00.630
This time, please don't cry, okay?

00:05:00.630 --> 00:05:02.040
I'm not crying.

00:05:03.240 --> 00:05:04.270
I refuse.

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:06.000
I won't let you die,

00:05:06.010 --> 00:05:06.950
Ying Du.

00:05:07.070 --> 00:05:08.900
Don't leave me.

00:05:09.510 --> 00:05:10.350
Zhaoli,

00:05:12.040 --> 00:05:13.720
I can't stay with you anymore.

00:05:14.270 --> 00:05:15.360
Don't leave me.

00:05:15.510 --> 00:05:16.350
But

00:05:16.950 --> 00:05:18.110
- Zhaoli,
- Please, no.

00:05:18.720 --> 00:05:20.510
