00:05:55.390 --> 00:05:56.390
Come back.

00:05:57.430 --> 00:05:59.600
Don't leave me alone.

00:06:05.480 --> 00:06:06.430
The Bracelet.

00:06:09.270 --> 00:06:10.240
The Bracelet...

00:06:10.720 --> 00:06:12.950
It can reverse time.

00:06:13.720 --> 00:06:15.270
Ying Du once used it to save me.

00:06:15.750 --> 00:06:17.190
As long as I activate it,

00:06:17.560 --> 00:06:19.120
I can bring Ying Du back to life.

00:06:31.360 --> 00:06:32.630
